    "attributes": {
        "action": "Add fire awareness to the national curriculum",
        "additional_details": "This should make people more aware of the risks of starting fires outdoors, and help to prevent devastating effects on our moorland and the environment as a whole.",
        "background": "The Government should require schools to teach children about the impact of fire on the environment, particularly moorland, and how it can affect fire services\u2019 ability to respond to other emergencies.",
